Title: 顶层代码结构
Describe: 文件从上到下分为：导入/常量 → 19 个功能模块 → 工具表 → Agent 主循环 → CLI 入口，每个模块以注释标题分隔。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
导入与依赖

[Description]
文件顶部（第1-37行）的导入结构：

**标准库**：`os`, `subprocess`, `json`, `time`, `random`, `threading`, `re`, `pathlib.Path`, `datetime`, `dataclasses`

**第三方**：
- `anthropic.Anthropic` — LLM API 客户端
- `dotenv.load_dotenv` — 环境变量加载
- `readline`（可选）— CLI 行编辑支持

**初始化**：
```python
client = Anthropic(base_url=os.getenv("ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL"))
MODEL = os.environ["MODEL_ID"]
PRIMARY_MODEL = MODEL
FALLBACK_MODEL = os.getenv("FALLBACK_MODEL_ID")
```

[UML]
@startuml
package "标准库" {
  [os / subprocess / json]
  [time / random / threading / re]
  [pathlib.Path / datetime]
  [dataclasses]
  [readline (optional)]
}

package "第三方" {
  [anthropic.Anthropic]
  [dotenv.load_dotenv]
}

package "初始化" {
  [client: Anthropic]
  [MODEL / PRIMARY_MODEL]
  [FALLBACK_MODEL]
  [WORKDIR = Path.cwd()]
}

[anthropic.Anthropic] --> [client: Anthropic]
[dotenv.load_dotenv] --> [MODEL / PRIMARY_MODEL]
@enduml

[Detail]
导入策略的特点：(1) 无任何内部模块导入——s20 是一个完全自包含的单文件；(2) `readline` 用 try/except 保护，确保在非交互环境中不报错；(3) `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` 允许用户指向兼容 API 端点。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
常量与配置

[Description]
关键配置常量（第39-54行）：

| 常量 | 值 | 作用 |
|------|------|------|
| `SKILLS_DIR` | `WORKDIR/"skills"` | Skill 文件扫描目录 |
| `TRANSCRIPT_DIR` | `WORKDIR/".transcripts"` | 压缩前的对话存档 |
| `DEFAULT_MAX_TOKENS` | 8000 | 常规 LLM 响应上限 |
| `ESCALATED_MAX_TOKENS` | 16000 | max_tokens 后升级 |
| `MAX_RETRIES` | 3 | 429/529 重试次数 |
| `CONTEXT_LIMIT` | 50000 | 触发压缩的字符阈值 |
| `KEEP_RECENT_TOOL_RESULTS` | 3 | micro_compact 保留数 |
| `PERSIST_THRESHOLD` | 30000 | 大输出写磁盘阈值 |
| `IDLE_POLL_INTERVAL` | 5 | Teammate 轮询间隔(s) |
| `IDLE_TIMEOUT` | 60 | Teammate 空闲超时(s) |

[UML]
@startuml
class "配置常量" as Config {
  WORKDIR : Path = Path.cwd()
  MODEL : str = environ["MODEL_ID"]
  PRIMARY_MODEL : str
  FALLBACK_MODEL : str | None
  --
  DEFAULT_MAX_TOKENS = 8000
  ESCALATED_MAX_TOKENS = 16000
  MAX_RETRIES = 3
  MAX_CONSECUTIVE_529 = 2
  MAX_RECOVERY_RETRIES = 2
  BASE_DELAY_MS = 500
  --
  CONTEXT_LIMIT = 50000
  KEEP_RECENT_TOOL_RESULTS = 3
  PERSIST_THRESHOLD = 30000
  --
  IDLE_POLL_INTERVAL = 5
  IDLE_TIMEOUT = 60
}
@enduml

[Detail]
这些常量控制了 Agent 的行为边界。`CONTEXT_LIMIT=50000` 字符（约 12k tokens）触发 `compact_history`；`PERSIST_THRESHOLD=30000` 确保超大工具输出写入磁盘而非留在内存。读者可修改这些值来观察 Agent 行为变化。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
模块布局概览

[Description]
文件按注释标题 `# ── Module Name ──` 划分为 19 个模块，从上到下的顺序是：

1. **Task System** (70-167) — 任务 CRUD 与依赖
2. **Worktree System** (170-280) — Git Worktree 隔离
3. **Skill Loading** (283-340) — 技能注册与加载
4. **Prompt Assembly** (342-373) — 系统提示组装
5. **Basic Tools** (376-468) — 基础工具函数
6. **MessageBus** (471-501) — 团队通信总线
7. **Protocol State** (504-546) — 协议请求/响应
8. **Autonomous Agent** (549-600) — 自治轮询
9. **Teammate Thread** (603-809) — 持久 Teammate
10. **Lead Protocol Tools** (824-853) — Lead 协议工具
11. **Hooks + Permission** (855-940) — 事件管道
12. **Subagent** (943-1033) — 一次性子代理
13. **Context Compaction** (1036-1148) — 上下文压缩
14. **Error Recovery** (1152-1201) — 错误恢复
15. **Background Tasks** (1204-1272) — 后台执行
16. **Cron Scheduler** (1275-1473) — 定时调度
17. **MCP System** (1476-1590) — 插件工具
18. **Tool Definitions** (1666-1835) — 工具注册表
19. **Agent Loop** (1855-2068) — 主循环 + CLI

[UML]
@startuml
package "s20_comprehensive.py (2069 lines)" {
  rectangle "导入 & 常量\n(1-68)" as imports #LightGray
  rectangle "Task System\n(70-167)" as task #LightBlue
  rectangle "Worktree System\n(170-280)" as wt #LightBlue
  rectangle "Skill Loading\n(283-340)" as skill #LightGreen
  rectangle "Prompt Assembly\n(342-373)" as prompt #LightGreen
  rectangle "Basic Tools\n(376-468)" as basic #LightYellow
  rectangle "MessageBus\n(471-501)" as bus #Pink
  rectangle "Protocol State\n(504-546)" as proto #Pink
  rectangle "Autonomous Agent\n(549-600)" as auto #Pink
  rectangle "Teammate Thread\n(603-809)" as teammate #Pink
  rectangle "Lead Protocol Tools\n(824-853)" as lead #Pink
  rectangle "Hooks + Permission\n(855-940)" as hooks #Wheat
  rectangle "Subagent\n(943-1033)" as sub #LightGreen
  rectangle "Context Compaction\n(1036-1148)" as compact #Orchid
  rectangle "Error Recovery\n(1152-1201)" as recovery #Orchid
  rectangle "Background Tasks\n(1204-1272)" as bg #LightBlue
  rectangle "Cron Scheduler\n(1275-1473)" as cron #LightBlue
  rectangle "MCP System\n(1476-1590)" as mcp #LightGreen
  rectangle "Tool Definitions\n(1666-1835)" as tools #LightYellow
  rectangle "Agent Loop + CLI\n(1855-2068)" as loop #Gold
}

imports -[hidden]d-> task
task -[hidden]d-> wt
wt -[hidden]d-> skill
skill -[hidden]d-> prompt
prompt -[hidden]d-> basic
basic -[hidden]d-> bus
bus -[hidden]d-> proto
proto -[hidden]d-> auto
auto -[hidden]d-> teammate
teammate -[hidden]d-> lead
lead -[hidden]d-> hooks
hooks -[hidden]d-> sub
sub -[hidden]d-> compact
compact -[hidden]d-> recovery
recovery -[hidden]d-> bg
bg -[hidden]d-> cron
cron -[hidden]d-> mcp
mcp -[hidden]d-> tools
tools -[hidden]d-> loop
@enduml

[Detail]
模块排列遵循**依赖顺序**：被依赖的模块在上，依赖者在下。例如 Task System 在最前因为 Worktree 和 Teammate 都引用它；Tool Definitions 在 Agent Loop 之前因为 loop 需要 `BUILTIN_TOOLS` 和 `BUILTIN_HANDLERS`。颜色分组：蓝=持久化，绿=扩展，粉=团队，紫=上下文/恢复，黄=工具，金=入口。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
入口逻辑

[Description]
文件末尾（第2034-2069行）的 `if __name__ == "__main__"` 入口：

```python
if __name__ == "__main__":
    CLI_ACTIVE = True
    history = []
    context = update_context({}, [])
    # 启动 cron 自动执行线程
    threading.Thread(target=cron_autorun_loop, ...).start()
    # REPL 循环
    while True:
        query = input(PROMPT)
        trigger_hooks("UserPromptSubmit", query)
        history.append({"role": "user", "content": query})
        with agent_lock:
            agent_loop(history, context)
            context = update_context(context, history)
            print_last_assistant(history)
        # 检查 inbox（teammate 消息）
        inbox = consume_lead_inbox(route_protocol=True)
```

[UML]
@startuml
start
:CLI_ACTIVE = True;
:初始化 history=[], context={};
:启动 cron_autorun_loop 守护线程;
:启动 cron_scheduler_loop 守护线程;

repeat
  :input(PROMPT) 等待用户输入;
  if (输入为 q/exit/空?) then (yes)
    stop
  endif
  :trigger_hooks("UserPromptSubmit", query);
  :history.append(user message);
  :acquire agent_lock;
  :agent_loop(history, context);
  :update_context(context, history);
  :print_last_assistant(history);
  :release agent_lock;
  :consume_lead_inbox() 检查团队消息;
  if (有 inbox 消息?) then (yes)
    :注入 inbox 到 history;
  endif
repeat while (True)
@enduml

[Detail]
入口逻辑的关键设计：(1) `agent_lock` 确保主循环和 `cron_autorun_loop` 不会同时调用 `agent_loop`；(2) `cron_autorun_loop` 在用户不输入时也能触发 Cron 任务；(3) 每次用户输入后都检查 inbox，让 teammate 的消息能及时展示。这个 REPL 结构就是整个 Agent 的"心跳"。
